title: 124: Compression Pants, Sissy Squats, Back to the Future & More...
description: Pump Head questions answered here! Sal, Adam & Justin cover your questions about giving nutritional advice to beginners, the value of compression pants, the dangers of sissy squats, going back in time and using 1/2 squats to help with max squats.
